      <br>
      Hello Everyone! <br>
This is a website where you can find the famous and inspirational quotes from figures in history.
This helps you to know the thinking and ideas of various famous personalities and hence improve your knowledge and 
gives you a better idea about certain things. People love to read quotes, because these are inspiring and motivating thoughts condensed into a few words.
 They are drops of wisdom concentrated into one or a few sentences, which can bring light and understanding into the soul of the reader. 
 They have the power to awaken hope, faith and inner strength, and also ambition and motivation.<br>
 You can even share these quotes on the social networking so that you never no one thought or one quote may change somebody's life. 
 Every man who knows how to read has it in his power to magnify himself, to multiply the ways in which he exists, to make his
  life full, significant and interesting. Hope you find this interesting!
